      "writtenOn": "2020-03-02T18:31:12Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "As for graphics.DRM.atomic_test, I\u0027m not very familiar with the content of the test, but it looks like actually \"drm_atomic\"?\n\nIf so, maybe, instead of renaming, introducing video_overlays, whose implementation is just drm_atomic, may work better?\n\nOther than that, your proposal makes sense to me.\nIt\u0027d be great if the implementation (i.e. in .go file), there\u0027s some explanation about the relationship between drm_atomic USE flag, and video_overlay (which is by coincidence).",
